        <abstract> 
<p>CD doubts that he will be able to do much more that is new, but cannot bear idleness. Has great amount of material on variation under nature, but so much has been published since the appearance of the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> that he doubts he has the power of mind to render the mass into a digested whole.</p> 
        </abstract>
